<br>
I'll also use it when it's convenient, and I know we're not gonna be put into a bad situation before it recycles, like when killing the yard trash in Sleepers Tomb.  It helps keep the clerics from gaining heal aggro, and makes us zip through the Ancient Sentry's a lot faster. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usunflowersxegony.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunflowers Xegony</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/20/02 1:29:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1417.topic&index=43>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   .</span><hr size=1> Last few times I used defensive:<br>
