<br>
Its just one of those things you have to play with and adjust to your level of play. Whether its conserving healers mana, controling massive dmg taken in AE pulls and tanking, or just plain avoiding an ass raping from Seru, you just gotta screw around with it =/<br>
<br>
Personally, i use it as a mana saver. We tend to have very few clerics at most raids, and it helps to increase their stamina. Also for AoW who IS tankable without Defensive... but it would take far too much mana to keep myself up for that long. 7k is NOT a ton of hps when its going down by the 1000's =/<br>
<br>
See how long you can go without it, and judge what you're tanking in comparison to your hps, and just go with what your instinct says =/ <p><img src="http://home.bellsouth.net/coDataImages/bellsouthpwp/Groups/8/8336/pages/19228/WebSigwTitle.jpg" border="0"><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=109026"  target="_blank">Magelo Profile</a>
