After about 3 raids in there I decided to try it without defense because I think it will train the Clerics and I think when we try Vindi one day that might come in very handy.<br>
Bottom line:<br>
Use defense when you think you need it,first time mob,emergencies etc. but try to do without once you get comfortable with a certain type of mob and think you can do without. <p>May the wolves guide your path<BR>
