And we have killed him with under 50 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usolinarinnoruuk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Solinar Innoruuk</A> at: 5/2/02 11:29:14 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usolinarinnoruuk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Solinar Innoruuk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 99<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/2/02 11:33:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1417.topic&index=53>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: ...</span><hr size=1> In our opinion, using 1 tank &gt; tank swapping whenever humanly possible.<br>
<br>
No downtime from lost damage output during tank swaps.<br>
<br>
No chance at lost aggro control (nobody can pull off a war with BoC with a 10-15 sec head start)<br>
<br>
Fight lasted about 8-9 minutes if I recall correctly. Fights with tank swapping last 12 or more minutes long depending on the guild and output.<br>
<br>
Clerics are the key on AoW, of that there is no doubt. I believe we had 9 on our flawless kill.  Good clerics can keep a 5500 HP warrior alive all the way through defensive vs AoW. GOod clerics can keep a 7k warrior with CS3 and CA1 alive for 9 straight minutes against AoW (with luck on back to back flurry rounds). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uogbasherfiggbukker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>OgbasherFiggbukker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 41<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/2/02 11:36:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1417.topic&index=54>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ogbasher.com/kitty.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: ...</span><hr size=1> if your looking at  CH chain, defensive no question.<br>
